survey.music_making: I had brief musical training on trumpet and trombone between the ages of 12 and 15 but nothing particularly serious. I was in school and church choirs from 8 to 16. I'm not a musician.
survey.activities: driving, exercising, walking, cycling, general chores, parties, holiday gatherings
survey.habit_change: I don't keep up with pop music anymore. I used to seek out more indie music and listen to whole albums more often.
survey.habits: I like to scan the radio while driving. For other activities, I usually go with automatic playlists. If I hear something new or different comes on that I like, I'll check out the artist and similar music. I'll listen to albums I liked when I was younger when the mood strikes me. I mostly listen to classical while I work.
